    dc:creator "Morales, Nicolás Gutiérrez; Moreno, Juan Sebastián; Karremans, Adam P.; Gil-Amaya, Karen" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Restrepia santanderensis (Orchidaceae: Pleurothallidinae), a new species from the western slope of the eastern Andes in Colombia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7983758>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7983760>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7983764>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7983770> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7983758>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Illustration of Restrepia santanderensis, A. Habit. B. Flower. C. Dissected perianth with magnified trichomes of the synsepal. D. Lip, column, ovary, floral bract in lateral view. E. Lip, lateral and adaxial view. F. Column in ventral view, without the anther G. Anther cap and pollinaria. Illustration by Nicolás Gutiérrez Morales and Sebastián Moreno from the holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7983758/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7983760>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Lankester composite dissection plate (LCDP) of Restrepia santanderensis. A. Habit. B. Flower. C. Dissected perianth with magnified trichomes of the synsepal. D. Lip and column, lateral view. E. Lip, adaxial view. F. Column in ventral view. Photographs by Nicolás Gutiérrez Morales, from the holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7983760/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7983764>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Restrepia santanderensis N. Gutiérrez & K. Gil-Amaya, and similar morphological species. A. R. flosculata. B. R. mendozae. C. R. santanderensis. D. Capsules of R. santanderensis. Photographs byAndreas Key (A), Joost Riksen (B) from cultivated specimens and Nicolás Gutiérrez Morales (C, D) from the paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7983764/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7983770>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. View of the Restrepia santanderensis habitat in the western slope of the eastern Andes in Colombia, near to the top of “La Humareda” waterfall, in La Belleza (Santander) municipality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7983770/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

